text: Natalie Christine Horler (born 23 September 1981 in Bonn, West Germany) is a German-born singer-songwriter of English origin. Her parents, David and Christine Horler, are English. She is the lead singer of the Eurodance dance- pop group Cascada. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:German pop singers Category:Musicians from Bonn Category:Synth-pop singers
